caption.text: It's the last day of #rcnanintendostacks week from the awesome @theretrocollectivena and it's anything goes day! Even though we had N64 stacks already I went for a different but still N64 stack because it's the anniversary of the US release and I just had to. Since moving to the US last year I've been buying games I enjoy playing and without realizing it was the N64 collection which took off the most. I have quite a few more boxes but they're in my storage unit for now, but obviously no one puts OoT, Perfect Dark or Paper Mario in storage! Here's to the N64 👏👏 #nintendo #n64 #nin10do #rceurope #retrocollectiveeurope #retrocollectivena #retro #classic #retrogamer #nintendo64 #perfectdark #zelda #tloz #link #ocarinaoftime #mario #supermario #luigi #retrogaming #retrofighters #cibsunday #collection #wii #wiiu #switch #nintendoswitch

Was going to wait until me next check to get this since money is tight, but ended up receiving it as a gift today.  Hell yes.

caption.text:
ICYMI (IN CASE YOU MISSED IT) Naughty Dog finally revealed the release date for the highly anticipated PS4 exclusive ‘The Last of Us Part II’.⁣⁣⁣
⁣⁣⁣
Naughty Dog also showed the special editions for the ‘The Last of Us Part II’, and according to the game’s description, the PS4 exclusive will be a 2-disc game.⁣⁣⁣
⁣⁣⁣
That’s gigantic.⁣⁣⁣
⁣⁣⁣
Neil Druckmann, the game’s director said that ‘The Last of Us Part II’ will be the most ambitious, longest, and biggest game that Naughty Dog has ever put together.⁣⁣⁣
⁣⁣⁣
"𝗪𝐞 𝐛𝐞𝐠𝐚𝐧 𝐰𝐨𝐫𝐤𝐢𝐧𝐠 𝐨𝐧 𝐭𝐡𝐢𝐬 𝐠𝐚𝐦𝐞 𝐨𝐯𝐞𝐫 𝐟𝐢𝐯𝐞 𝐲𝐞𝐚𝐫𝐬 𝐚𝐠𝐨. 𝐈𝐭’𝐬 𝐡𝐚𝐫𝐝 𝐭𝐨 𝐝𝐞𝐬𝐜𝐫𝐢𝐛𝐞 𝐭𝐡𝐞 𝐢𝐦𝐦𝐞𝐧𝐬𝐞 𝐩𝐫𝐞𝐬𝐬𝐮𝐫𝐞 𝐨𝐟 𝐟𝐨𝐥𝐥𝐨𝐰𝐢𝐧𝐠 𝐮𝐩 𝐭𝐡𝐞 𝐟𝐢𝐫𝐬𝐭 𝐠𝐚𝐦𝐞. [...] 𝗪𝐡𝐚𝐭 𝐰𝐞 𝐫𝐞𝐚𝐥𝐢𝐳𝐞𝐝 𝐩𝐫𝐞𝐭𝐭𝐲 𝐞𝐚𝐫𝐥𝐲 𝐨𝐧 𝐢𝐬 𝐭𝐡𝐚𝐭 𝐰𝐞 𝐰𝐞𝐫𝐞 𝐩𝐮𝐭𝐭𝐢𝐧𝐠 𝐭𝐨𝐠𝐞𝐭𝐡𝐞𝐫 𝐍𝐚𝐮𝐠𝐡𝐭𝐲 𝐃𝐨𝐠’𝐬 𝐦𝐨𝐬𝐭 𝐚𝐦𝐛𝐢𝐭𝐢𝐨𝐮𝐬 𝐚𝐧𝐝 𝐥𝐨𝐧𝐠𝐞𝐬𝐭 𝐠𝐚𝐦𝐞 𝐢𝐧 𝐨𝐮𝐫 𝟑𝟓 𝐲𝐞𝐚𝐫 𝐡𝐢𝐬𝐭𝐨𝐫𝐲. 𝐓𝐨 𝐭𝐞𝐥𝐥 𝐭𝐡𝐢𝐬 𝐤𝐢𝐧𝐝 𝐨𝐟 𝐬𝐭𝐨𝐫𝐲 𝐭𝐡𝐞 𝐠𝐚𝐦𝐞 𝐧𝐞𝐞𝐝𝐞𝐝 𝐭𝐨 𝐛𝐞 𝐦𝐚𝐬𝐬𝐢𝐯𝐞.”⁣⁣⁣
⁣⁣⁣
That’s really great news. ⁣⁣⁣
⁣⁣⁣
To put it in context, 2013’s ‘The Last of Us’ won over 200 Game of the Year awards, and the studio is yet to release a game that doesn't immediately become critically and commercially acclaimed.⁣⁣⁣⁣

Mortal Kombat 3 (MK3) is a fighting video game developed by Midway / Atari Games and first released into arcades in 1995 as the third game in the Mortal Kombat series. As in the previous games, it has a cast of characters that players choose from and guide through a series of battles against other opponents. The game avoids the tournament storyline of its predecessors, as various warriors instead fight against the returning Shao Kahn, who has resurrected his bride Sindel and started an invasion of Earthrealm. caption.text: Last post for the week of #shmupsareshooters hosted by our leader @turbothunder16 🤘🏻 what glorious week it was where we took a hashtag with 0 mentions to now 500+ 💪🏼 I want to give thanks to every soldier mentioned and also maybe some I've missed (let me know and I'll add) 🙏🙏 Thanks for allowing a newbie to shmups like me to post and join on the fun. Mon royaume... Du moins une partie ❤️ Je suis fan des mangas depuis bien longtemps mais les jeux vidéos je dirais que ca fait encore plus longtemps que les Mangas...
J'ai commencé au tout début par la Gameboy advance, puis ensuite la Gameboy advance sp mais j'avais que quelques jeux... Pas très connu de tous mais j'ai beaucoup aimé !! #warioland4 #inspecteurgadjet et ensuite j'ai eu beaucoup de ds... Je sais pas comment mais ma mère voulait toute les avoir... Du coup je suis entrée dans le monde de Nintendo à ce moment là avec Kirby, Pokémon etc. Et après je me suis mise à la ps2, game cube et ps3... Puis ps4, et switch... 3ds aujourd'hui... Enfin une vrai aventure qui m'a fait aimer les jeux vidéos ❤️🕹️ sans les jeux.. Je sais pas ce que je ferais

caption.text:
For those unfamiliar with the character, Madame Web first appeared in The Amazing Spider-Man #210 back in 1980. Real name Cassandra Webb, she was born as a mutant in Salem, Oregon. Plagued with a neuromuscular disease which rendered her paralyzed and blind, Webb makes up for it with strong psychic abilities such as precognition, telepathy and clairvoyance, in one occasion helping Spidey locate a kidnapped victim. Madame Web earned her moniker from the life-support machine she’s constantly hooked onto due to her disease, which resembles a giant spider web.

I would like to thank Hugo @inateck for sending me this AMAZING Shockproof Nintendo Switch case! I have used it for a few weeks now, and it has met my standards as a case I would use to protect my Nintendo Switch! 
My requirements for an excellent case:

1. Good protection (drop protection ‘cause I’m clumsy)
2. Room for power cords and/or accessories. 
3. Game compartment (this one holds 20 game) 
4. Comfortable to carry (i.e strap or handle again, ‘cause I’m clumsy)

One of the simple, yet often missed features about carrying cases are the external strap or handle to make it easier to carry. Often, I only see the sleeves in the stores, which do an ok job, but I end up placing it inside another bag. The Inateck case HAS the strap. 🙌🏾 Another cool feature are the groves for the for the triggers so it fits perfectly inside the case (extra protection). Additional there is a Velcro strap to security hold your Switch in place in. They also include a cloth for the screen...a very nice little bonus. 
________________________________________________

More info direct from Inateck: 【Enhanced Protection】Three-layer protection - A hard shell covered by external felt cloth and internal flannelette lining, keeps your device safe from shock and scratches. A band is equipped to secure your Switch from sliding. 【Large Capacity】The case has 20 game cartridges, and a mesh bag that can hold Joy-Con Straps, a charging cable, power bank etc. 【Optimized Design】The bottom is designed with a concave slot that fits your Switch better and relieves pressure on the Joy-Con button. To prevent a zipper from scratching your device, the accessory pouch is closed by an elastic band.

caption.text:
Did you go to the eshop and download yourself a copy of Gold Silver or Crystal? 
Only getting the Red Gyradose as your first shiny? And want more? 
What if i told you that in Gen 2 you can breed a shiny with a non shiny Pokemon
Turning your odds from 1/8192 to 1/64 through breeding? ---
Shiny hunting feels impossible through gen 2 and onward to some of us because of how high the odds are and theres no shiny charm till black and white 2.

Well In gen 2 theres something in the coding that makes Breeding a shiny with a mon shiny pop out shinies a bit faster 
I believe its only breeding males with females of the same species or egg group

Anyway. 
So you may not have a shiny ditto yet 
Theres two ways to get one
Random encounter one
Or Use your red gyradose to trade to red blue or yellow use on a ditto only with mimic then catch and trade back to gsc 
If you just have the Shiny Gyradose what can you breed with it? 
One example is Dragonair 
Another Tentacruel

A helpful thing to know is your egg groups

Gyradose is in the Water 2 and dragon egg group
Dragonair is in the Dragon egg group
Ekans is in the field and dragon egg group
Tentacruel is in the water 2 egg group
Ekans can breed with any field egg group mon such as mankey and primeape even eevee

I have done this shiny hunt method myself
Getting myself various Shiny Pokemon

Since theres no abilities eggs will hatch relatively slow

Some hatch faster than others such as Magikarp hatching faster than lapras or snorlax

So my suggestion is trying magikarp first test your patience
Then try Dratini or Something else.

If you're like "woah shit is this true?" Dm me and I'll provide video links /)

GTA V je akciona avantura u otvorenom svetu. Igra se odvija u fiktivnom  svetu San Andreas, a inspiracija je Južna Kalifornija. Igrač slobodno  može da se kreće po svetu kao i gradu Los Santosu (zamena za Los Angeles). Igra može da se igra iz prvog ili trećeg lica, a glavni junak  se kreće peške ili u vozilu. Glavni junak hara San Andreasom, a većina  misija uključuje pucanje i vožnju. Igrači koji prilikom igre čine zločin  iniciraće odgovarajuću reakciju pravosuđa. To će se meriti tzv. "wanted" sistemom. Dodatak igri je multiplejer mod GTA Online koji daje  mogućnost da se do 30 igrača uključi u kooperativne ili takmičarske  mečeve. Dugo iščekivana, GTA 5 je oborila sve rekorde po prodavanosti  širom sveta, a pokupila je i sve pohvale za dizajn igrača, otvorenog  sveta, kao i sam gameplay. Od prelaska sa parkura i jedinstvenim interakcijama sa okolinom, do novog borbenog i blockbuster akcione borbe, to je Spider-Man, za razliku od bilo kog koga ste prethodno igrali. Sony Interactive Entertainment, Insomniac Games i Marvel udružili su se kako bi stvorili potpuno novu i autentičnu avanturu Spider-Man. Ovo nije Spider-Man kog ste upoznali ili ste ikada videli. Ovo je iskusni Peter Parker koji je više majstorski izvežban u borbi protiv velikog kriminala u New Yorku. Istvremeno se nastoji uravnotežiti sa svojim haotičnim privatnim životom i karijerom dok se sudbina miliona njujorčana oslanja na njegova ramena.

So... Today I hit the big 3 0. And during the three decades I have been alive I must say that life tends to get better, even when it has been terrible. 
Today, my lovely wife gave me a present despite me asking her not to while we were away, but I was over the moon about this little Switch! Then we spent the day in Rhodes Town and had a blast, especially since due to some world heritage thing, all museums were free, so we got to see some ancient history for free! Some objects dated back to 700 b.c! 
Today was great, I got to see ancient history, a lot of cute and amazing cats (and two dogs!) As well as have a lovely dinner with my love.

19 - 23 Links Awakening
23 - 01 Smash Bros Ultimate 
01 - 05 Jedi Knight 2
05 - 09 Dark Souls Remastered
09 - 11 Mario Kart 8
11 - 13 Smash Bros Ultimate 
13 - 17 Final Fantasy VIII Remaster 
17 - 19 Super Mario Maker 2

#MilanGamesWeek2019 🎮
Si è da poco conclusa l’edizione 2019 di #MilanGamesWeek. Un’edizione per certi versi un po’ “ridotta” rispetto agli ultimi anni, con poche anteprime ed esclusive da provare. A farla da padrone è stata @playstationit con un’area molto vasta e con due titoli molto interessanti da poter giocare in anteprima, #FinalFantasyVIIRemake e #MarvelsAvengers. Non da meno sono state @nintendoswitchitalia con la possibilità di provare #PokemonSpadaScudo e #LuigisMansion3, e @xboxitalia con la prova in anteprima di #GhostReconBreakpoint in collaborazione con @ubisoftitalia. Piccolo stand ma non meno importante quello di @bethesda_it che offriva l’anteprima di #DoomEternal. Per il resto poche altre novità e meno tornei di eSports rispetto allo scorso anno.
Appuntamento al prossimo con la speranza di vedere ancora più anteprime!

caption.text:
Los Donkey Kong Country son mis plataformas favoritos.
.
Me enamoré de estos monos con DKC2 Diddy's Kong Quest en SNES que pude conocer gracias a un amigo con la consola ya que yo no tenía. Me parece el mejor de esa trilogía y me lo he pasado un montón de veces, sacando siempre que puedo el 102%.
.
Yo jugué a esta trilogía desordenada, porque el primer DKC fue el último que llegó a mis manos. Me gustó menos que los otros por eso, porque sus secuelas mejoraban la fórmula y se echaban cosas en falta en esta primera entrega al jugarla por primera vez después.
.
Me alegró mucho que Nintendo recuperara la saga en Wii, aunque compuse catar DKC Returns hasta que salió la versión 3D para Nintendo 3DS, la cual me volví a comprar (tras vender un primer modelo que tuve) por esté juegazo ya que no tenía Wii.
.
También me ilusionó mucho que sacaran el Tropical Freeze de WiiU en Switch ya que tampoco tengo WiiU pero sí Switch. Este me avergüenza reconocer que no lo he acabado... 😥
.
